                     <section id="archimateObjectClass">
                        <title>archimateObjectClass</title>
                        <para/>
                        <table class="elementtable">
                           <tr>
                              <td class="starter" valign="top">ArchimateObjectClass</td>
                              <td class="starter" valign="top">An objectclass predefined by Archi.<para/>This does not show up in the policy file explicitly. Used to have a starting point to generate/document the objectClass hierarchy.</td>
                           </tr>
