                                    </tr>
                                    <tr>
                                       <td>attribute:maxOccurs</td>
                                       <td>1</td>
                                    </tr>
                                 </table>
                              </td>
                           </tr>
                           <tr>
                              <td class="starter" valign="top">structural</td>
                              <td class="starter" valign="top">If the value of this property is "true", then the property is structural:<para/>The value will be generated by a default associated to it, and it is an error to enter the value into the model through some properties.<para/>FIXME: this check is not implemented yet.<para/>The property is represented by the attribute with the same name in the policy file.</td>
                           </tr>
                           <tr>
                              <td> </td>
